<![CDATA[<span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 12px;">Hi&nbsp;<i>(<span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);">client name</span>)</i>,<br><br>We’re excited to be able to offer you the ability to collect reviews and monitor your online presence directly through the OutRank dashboard. By gathering reviews from your happy customers, you can help improve your credibility online by showcasing these reviews on Rate-A-Biz.com as well as your website. Below are the instructions on how to request and monitor reviews in the dashboard.</span></span><ul style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><li><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12px;">Log in at live.rogersoutrank.com</span></span></li><li><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12px;">Click on Web Presence then Reviews on the left hand navigation bar</span></span><br></li><li><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12px;">Enter the email addresses of the customers you want to request from and hit “Request Reviews”</span></span></li><li><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12px;">If you have already requested reviews, click on the “Request Reviews” button on the top right</span></span></li><ul><li><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12px;">Enter the customer’s email address in the “To” field and hit “Send Now”</span></span></li></ul></ul><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 12px;">And if you’re out of the office or on a job site with a customer, you can quickly request reviews from your smartphone. To do this, simply open up your dashboard from your smartphone, log in, hit “Collect a Review”, and hand your phone over to the customer to finish the rest!<br><br></span></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 12px;">You’re all set. Follow these simple steps anytime you want to request or take action with your reviews. If you have any questions at all, please contact us directly at&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;">(866) 269-1710</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 12px;">.<br><br>Thanks so much and have a great day!</span></span><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12px;"><br></span></span></div><div><div><font face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: 12px;"><b>Customer Support</b></span></font></div><div><font face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: 12px;"><b>OutRank by Rogers</b></span></font></div><div><font face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: 12px;">(866) 269-1710</span></font></div><div><font face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: 12px;">outranksupport@service.rogersoutrank.com</span></font></div></div>]]></td>
